Name: Search recipe
Actors: Users with accounts
Goals: Return a recipe with the most familiar content selected by the user
Preconditions: User must have an account and have inputted search criteria
Summary: User searches database and is provided a recipe matching their inputted criteria
Related use case: View Recipe
Steps: Actors - System Response
1. Requests to search a recipe - 2. Asks for the user to input search criteria
3. Inputs search criteria - 4. Prompt the selection of confirmation/ canceling the search
5. Choose confirm or cancel to search for matching recipe - 6. Returns a recipe with the most familiar search content
Postconditions: The selected recipe(s) should be deleted from the recipe database
